<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <div class="about-img-wrap fade-up">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1619642751034-765dfdf7c58e?w=800&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Friendly auto mechanic in shop" />
        <div class="about-img-overlay"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="fade-up">
        <span class="section-label">Our Story</span>
        <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom:28px;">A Shop Built on Trust, Not Transactions.</h2>
        <p>TrueNorth Auto wasn't built overnight. It was built one car at a time, one honest conversation at a time. When we opened our doors on Yonge Street, we had one goal: be the kind of shop that people actually feel good about bringing their car to.</p>
        <p>We know how stressful car trouble can be. The last thing you need is a mechanic who talks over your head, pads your bill, or tells you everything needs replacing. That's not how we operate. We'll always tell you what your car actually needs — and what it can wait on.</p>
        <p>Over the years, we've become a go-to for families all across North York and East York. Some of our customers have been bringing their cars to us for over a decade. That kind of loyalty is something we take seriously — and work hard every day to deserve.</p>
        <div class="about-signature">— The TrueNorth Auto Team</div>
        <div style="margin-top:28px;">
          <a href="tel:+14167339388" class="btn btn-outline-dark">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.61 1.13h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.72a16 16 0 0 0 6.29 6.29l.96-.96a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
            Meet the Team — Call Us
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

